{"tid":211644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］左手手背對落有一粒黑點","createTime":"2017-04-21T18:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T10:13:53.000Z","uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7de29d86bb5af5a07622708f8b857ef14357cb21","tid":211644,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"我左手手背果個位好耐之前生左粒黑點出嚟，比啲皮包住嘅，初初無咩點理佢。<br />\n之後佢愈嚟愈大粒，我試過整開塊皮，整下粒黑點，質感好似結左焦嘅傷口咁。<br />\n上網Google 過，啲result好似唔係幾match 我呢個case。<br />\n有無醫科巴打出嚟講下粒野係咩嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef1a003eaf764d6c22154894791b07dd3a35705","tid":211644,"uid":39700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"墨囉<br />\n吊你"},{"pid":"80f5b143ec02a752a28dd157fc7b7f1c7635684d","tid":211644,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:41:23.000Z","msg":"驗下係咪皮膚癌"},{"pid":"c8259f6b9936920ff5e92449422546fcea545018","tid":211644,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>墨囉<br />\n吊你</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係墨，佢係深黑色"},{"pid":"835ed5c5129a343cfaf613ba5926ab4691d43739","tid":211644,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>墨囉<br />\n吊你</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係墨，佢係深黑色</blockquote><br />\n黑色有分深定淺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa26fddbe3eabc888f6bb7bd849580a949008c92","tid":211644,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驗下係咪皮膚癌</blockquote><br />\n我Google都見到關於皮膚癌嘅reault<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望唔好係<br />\n但係大多數 都係話皮膚癌係多啲，一生就生幾粒，我就係零零舍舍有一粒<br />\n而且我上癌症基金會個網睇，會中皮膚癌嘅人嘅特徵，我一個都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d77a5a06b9e69f9d5fcd430370ab1927584f84","tid":211644,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>墨囉<br />\n吊你</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係墨，佢係深黑色</blockquote><br />\n黑色有分深定淺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁黑色真係有分別既"},{"pid":"3ab374ffed6674a0d7d0ef26dc2971b812ea5747","tid":211644,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"影張相出黎啦屌你<br />\n純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed22ec52b92ea32752c1aee432e47607292a6ea","tid":211644,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b5wcqt0j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb5wcqt0j&h=9734569e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w1k4pn9r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw1k4pn9r&h=c8eee29f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ef5b443bb70d589cbecd8daccbff90866c1b7ca","tid":211644,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"有無人知咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dc58ee7600ac9c5d515c0d394bd8bf4577028f","tid":211644,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"似皮膚癌/死人斑，不過都係睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"3a5d50021387c2a2c3fc005dc30c7696fcb43bdd","tid":211644,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係掛"}]}